Source code :
LDA 4000H      ; Load A with the contents of 4000H
MOV B, A       ; Copy A into register B
LDA 4001H      ; Load A with the contents of 4001H
ADD B          ; Add contents of B to A
STA 4002H      ; Store result at 4002H
HLT            ; Terminate program

